i/build/modules/:name Method: GET Parameters: name (string) Module name. Default value: name . Required. Example request (curl): code curl --user &lt;username&gt;:&lt;password&gt; \ -X GET \ https://hub.cfengine.com/api/build/modules/autorun Successful response example: code HTTP 200 OK { &quot;name&quot;: &quot;autorun&quot;, &quot;readme&quot;: &quot;&lt;h1 id=\&quot;enable-autorun\&quot;&gt;Enable autorun&lt;/h1&gt;
